![Christ of Vung Tau](https://statics.vinpearl.com/vung-tau-jesus-statue-6_1687677415.jpg)  
[Hình ảnh: Christ of Vung Tau]  
*Wear proper clothes if you want to visit inside the Statue (Source: Collected)*  
For the best Vung Tau tour to discover Vung Tau Christ Statue, remember some tips:  
- Prepare a lightweight sun-protective jacket, and a hat to avoid being sun-burnt;
- Choose comfortable and respectful attire that covers your knees and has sleeves;
- Bring bottled water to stay hydrated. Avoid overpacking to make it easier to climb the stairs;
- Remove your shoes and leave your belongings outside when you arrive at the statue of Jesus. There will be someone to watch over them for you;
- When you reach the hands of the statue, each visitor is usually allowed to stay for 5-10 minutes to give others a chance;
